Usage: define_proc_arguments [-help] <command_name> [-define_args <string>]
                             [-hide] [-info <string>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<command_name>            # command name to be defined (string, required)
-define_args <string>     # argument definition list (string, optional)
-hide                     # hide command name and body (bool, optional)
-info <string>            # Provides help information for the procedure
                          # (string, optional)